2. **Comparison of model-predicted cues vs. ground-truth cues**: The emotion cue grounding analysis is purely qualitative. Show side-by-side: what Deaf annotators identified vs. what models claim to see, with quantitative evaluation (e.g., overlap between mentioned cues).

